ip




--------------------------------------------
link
--------------------------------------------
ip link set <dev> up/down

set <dev> mtu xxx

更改网卡代号 Mac 地址需要先关闭网卡
set <dev> name <newname>

set <interface> address <new_mac_address>


添加虚拟接口
add <interface> type <type> [options] 


删除接口
delete <interface> 





--------------------------------------------
addr
--------------------------------------------
ip addr add <ip_address>/<prefix_length> dev <interface>

ip addr add <ip_address>/<prefix_length> dev <interface>







--------------------------------------------
route
--------------------------------------------


route add default via <gateway>


route add <network>/<prefix_length> via gateway

route del
